headline: EQT Increases Base Dividend by Five Percent
summary: EQT Corporation (NYSE: EQT) today announced that its Board of Directors declared a quarterly cash dividend on its common stock of $0.165 per share, payable on December 1, 2025, to shareholders of record at the close of business on November 5, 2025. This represents a five percent increase to EQT's regular quarterly cash dividend to $0.66 per share on an annualized basis.
